{"tid":1384021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到有人玩分化 重申一次 最緊要係合理壞疑","createTime":"2019-07-29T22:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T23:08:27.000Z","uid":216008,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88f8c2072a16d3f1fa34fdbc27cadb51a78c233e","tid":1384021,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:39:14.000Z","msg":"一嚟就屌人係鬼，一係你本身就係鬼，一係你唔識表達<br />\n我只想講，每樣野大家都唔可以信到十足，要有對事情既壞疑，咁先可以免被其他人帶風向，有呢種壞疑，先可以貫徹自己既信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分不割不督</span></strong><br />\n雖則兄弟爬山，但如果見到同路人真係變得極端而呢種極端係對運動無幫助，都請用心同佢傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454607ab923f085f0ef148a3a7aed8dccd0612b7","tid":1384021,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:40:20.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c09ac3f597d8aa69dda3910d7f29907543cbeb8","tid":1384021,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:42:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"488b94ba5b8e2ee1491c346c0fd1d8a1cd1386d8","tid":1384021,"uid":36158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都要用"},{"pid":"c4838ebc636f4742e175590085eda23d096d16b6","tid":1384021,"uid":66221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:43:18.000Z","msg":"多撚咗好多鬼係度搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea